# ───── SERVER‑ONLY ─────────────────────────────────────────
# Main Prisma URL – session pooler (IPv4) keeps idle connections cheap
# Format: postgresql://[user[:password]@][host][:port][/database][?parameters]
# Example: "postgresql://postgres:password@aws-0-eu-central-1.pooler.supabase.com:5432/postgres?sslmode=require"
